lxvbBPENQ0JQedIKA">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ nhất đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第一段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%ADn/T%E1%BB%91ng-D%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%8Dc-quan-quy-La-Giang/poem-0xYsnb1E0vMhiUd5M18fSw">Tống Dư học quan quy La Giang - 送余學官歸羅江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-eBGdtm3O4c2NQ7sIhikeXg">Dương Thận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-III/poem-EsyilYBXJVcg5eoS7vsfEA">Vô đề (III) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/author-bg2Iw4F0Q1WB-Vf8_0Kqcw">Khả Mân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-VIII/poem-b9bfpT6s32OOh4k3tcSlrw">Vô đề (VIII) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-VNhahLxtqyIrLeDASL0s9Q">Thực Hiền</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Xu%C3%A2n-tuy%E1%BA%BFt/poem-ApNO5j2eGXWXrA4UQdLE7w">Xuân tuyết - 春雪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br></div>	</div>
